\begin_layout Description
Q: What versions of LyX are supported?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
A: The tool is slowly improving; it now should work with LyX versions 1.5.5
 to 1.6.2.
 It has been tested on Linux, Mac OS X and Windows.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Q: What can we expect from the tool in the future?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
A: eLyXer should support a widening set of LyX features, and a couple of
 tricks of its own (such as page segmenting).
 Eventually it should be recognized LyX so that it can be accessed from
 within the editor.
 Joint distribution is also a possibility.
\end_layout

